Package: ripple
Title: Replicate-Aware Inference of Paracrine Profiles via Likelihood Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Carolina", "Mangana", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cmangana@cemm.at")
Description: Detects distance-dependent gene expression gradients from any
    query cell type in spatial transcriptomics data. For each gene in each
    target cell type, fits a per-sample Poisson GLM with cell-size offset,
    then combines across replicates via Fisher's combined p-value with sign
    consistency gating. Supports confounder control, permutation testing,
    pathway enrichment, and ligand-receptor integration.
